(317, 'Spy', 'Chernin Entertainment', 'Released', '1.0', 'LBX', '29.99', 'PG', 2015, 'Action', '1.85:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A desk-bound CIA analyst volunteers to go undercover to infiltrate the world of a deadly arms dealer, and prevent diabolical global disaster.'),
(318, 'Escape From L.A.', 'Paramount', 'Released', '5.1', 'LBX', '29.99', 'R', 1996, 'Action', '2.35:1', 18, 1, 5, 0, 'This time, a cataclysmic temblor hits Los Angeles, turning it into an island. The president views the quake as a sign from above, expels Los Angeles from the country and makes it a penal colony for those found guilty of moral crimes. When his daughter, part of a resistance movement, steals the control unit for a doomsday weapon, Snake again gets tapped to save the day.'),
