(320, 'A Bugs Life', 'Pixar', 'Released', '5.1', 'LBX, 16:9', '14.98', 'R', 1998, 'Adventure', '1.85:1', 1, 0, 0, 0, 'On behalf of "oppressed bugs everywhere," an inventive ant named Flik hires a troupe of warrior bugs to defend his bustling colony from a horde of freeloading grasshoppers led by the evil-minded Hopper.'),
