(599, 'Long Kiss Goodnight', 'The Steve Tisch Company', 'Released', '5.1', '4:3, LBX, 16:9', '24.98', 'R', 1996, 'Crime', '2.35:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Samantha Caine, suburban homemaker, is the ideal mom to her 8 year old daughter Caitlin. She lives in Honesdale, PA, has a job teaching school and makes the best Rice Krispie treats in town. But when she receives a bump on her head, she begins to remember small parts of her previous life as a lethal, top-secret agent.'),
