(686, 'Best In Show', 'Castle Rock Entertainment', 'Released', '5.1', 'LBX, 16:9', '24.98', 'PG-13', 2000, 'Comedy', '1.85:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The tension is palpable, the excitement is mounting and the heady scent of competition is in the air as hundreds of eager contestants from across America prepare to take part in what is undoubtedly one of the greatest events of their lives -- the Mayflower Dog Show. The canine contestants and their owners are as wondrously diverse as the great country that has bred them.'),
(687, 'Clockwork Orange', 'Warner Bros. Pictures', 'Released', '5.1', '4:3', '24.98', 'R', 1971, 'Science Fiction', '1.33:1', 1, 0, 0, 0, 'In a near-future Britain, young Alexander DeLarge and his pals get their kicks beating and raping anyone they please. When not destroying the lives of others, Alex swoons to the music of Beethoven. The state, eager to crack down on juvenile crime, gives an incarcerated Alex the option to undergo an invasive procedure thatll rob him of all personal agency. In a time when conscience is a commodity, can Alex change his tune?'),
(688, 'Dungeons And Dragons', 'New Line Cinema', 'Released', '5.1', 'LBX', '24.98', 'PG-13', 2000, 'Action', '1.85:1', 20, 1, 3, 0, 'The classic role-playing game comes to life in this magical adventure. The empire of Izmer is a divided land: Elite magicians called Mages rule while lowly commoners are powerless. When Empress Savina (Thora Birch) vows to bring equality and prosperity to her land, the evil Mage Profion (Jeremy Irons) plots to depose her. But this good-vs.-evil battle is no game!'),
(689, 'Full Metal Jacket', 'Natant', 'Released', '5.1', '4:3', '24.98', 'R', 1987, 'Drama', '1.33:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A pragmatic U.S. Marine observes the dehumanizing effects the U.S.-Vietnam War has on his fellow recruits from their brutal boot camp training to the bloody street fighting in Hue.'),
(690, 'Game Of Death ', 'Philippe Martinez Productions', 'Released', '2.0', 'LBX', '19.98', 'R', 2010, 'Adventure', '2.35:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'CIA agent Marcus is sent undercover to Detroit to take out an arms dealer and the head of the hedge fund that is financing him. His CIA backup has other plans and turns on him, and its a fight to survive in a hospital and into the hedge fund vault.'),
(691, 'The Wrong Missy', 'Happy Madison Productions', 'Released', '5.1', '4:3', '24.98', 'NR', 2020, 'Comedy', '1.33:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A guy meets the woman of his dreams and invites her to his companys corporate retreat, but realizes he sent the invite to the wrong person.'),
(692, 'Nutty Professor 2: The Klumps', 'Universal Pictures', 'Released', '5.1/DTS', 'LBX, 16:9', '26.98', 'NR', 2000, 'Fantasy', '1.85:1', 2, 0, 0, 0, 'The hilarity begins when professor Sherman Klump finds romance with fellow DNA specialist, Denise Gaines, and discovers a brilliant formula that reverses aging. But Shermans thin and obnoxious alter ego, Buddy Love, wants out...and a big piece of the action. And when Buddy gets loose, things get seriously nutty.'),
(693, 'Pay It Forward', 'Bel Air Entertainment', 'Released', '5.1', 'LBX, 16:9', '24.98', 'PG-13', 2000, 'Drama', '1.85:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Like some other kids, 12-year-old Trevor McKinney believed in the goodness of human nature. Like many other kids, he was determined to change the world for the better. Unlike most other kids, he succeeded.'),
(694, 'Me Before You', 'New Line Cinema', 'Released', '2.0', '4:3', '24.98', 'UR', 2016, 'Drama', '1.33:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A small town girl is caught between dead-end jobs. A high-profile, successful man becomes wheelchair bound following an accident. The man decides his life is not worth living until the girl is hired for six months to be his new caretaker. Worlds apart and trapped together by circumstance, the two get off to a rocky start. But the girl becomes determined to prove to the man that life is worth living and as they embark on a series of adventures together, each finds their world changing in ways neither of them could begin to imagine.'),
(695, 'Top Gunner', 'The Asylum', 'Released', '2.0', '4:3', '24.98', 'UR', 2020, 'Action', '1.33:1', 1, 0, 0, 0, 'Recent graduates of a secluded U.S. Air Force base must protect a gene-editing bioweapon from the Russian militaryâ€”who are desperate to seize the deadly viral agent at any cost.'),
(696, 'Shining', 'Hawk Films', 'Released', '5.1', '4:3', '24.98', 'R', 1980, 'Horror', '1.33:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Jack Torrance accepts a caretaker job at the Overlook Hotel, where he, along with his wife Wendy and their son Danny, must live isolated from the rest of the world for the winter. But they arent prepared for the madness that lurks within.'),
(698, 'Futurama: Into the Wild Green Yonder', 'The Curiosity Company', 'Released', '1.0', '4:3', '19.99', 'NR', 2009, 'Animation', '1.33:1', 5, 1, 0, 0, 'Leela becomes an outlaw when she and a group of ecologically-minded feminists attempt to save an asteroid of primitive life forms and the Violet Dwarf star from being destroyed, while Fry joins a secret society and attempts to stop a mysterious species known as the "Dark Ones" from destroying all life in the universe.'),
(699, 'Star Trek Beyond', 'Skydance Media', 'Released', '1.0', '4:3', '19.99', 'NR', 2016, 'Action', '1.33:1', 3, 0, 0, 0, 'The USS Enterprise crew explores the furthest reaches of uncharted space, where they encounter a mysterious new enemy who puts them and everything the Federation stands for to the test.'),
(700, 'X-Men', 'The Donners Company', 'Released', '2.0', '4:3', '24.98', 'NR', 2016, 'Action', '1.33:1', 3, 0, 0, 0, 'After the re-emergence of the worlds first mutant, world-destroyer Apocalypse, the X-Men must unite to defeat his extinction level plan.'),
(701, 'X-Men 2', 'The Donners Company', 'Released', '2.0', '4:3', '24.98', 'NR', 2016, 'Action', '1.33:1', 5, 0, 0, 0, 'After the re-emergence of the worlds first mutant, world-destroyer Apocalypse, the X-Men must unite to defeat his extinction level plan.'),
(702, 'Interstellar', 'Legendary Entertainment', 'Released', '5.1', '4:3', '24.98', 'R', 2014, 'Adventure', '1.33:1', 1, 0, 0, 0, 'The adventures of a group of explorers who make use of a newly discovered wormhole to surpass the limitations on human space travel and conquer the vast distances involved in an interstellar voyage.'),
(703, 'Save The Last Dance', 'MTV Films', 'Released', '5.1', 'LBX, 16:9', '29.99', 'PG-13', 2001, 'Drama', '1.85:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A white midwestern girl moves to Chicago, where her new boyfriend is a black teen from the South Side with a rough, semi-criminal past.'),
(704, 'You Can Count On Me ', 'Crush Entertainment', 'Released', '5.0', 'LBX, 16:9', '29.99', 'R', 2000, 'Drama', '1.85:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A single mothers life is thrown into turmoil after her struggling, rarely-seen younger brother returns to town.'),
(705, 'Forever Mine', 'Moonstar Enterainment', 'Released', 'SUR', '4:3', '24.98', 'R', 1999, 'Crime', '1.33:1', 1, 0, 0, 0, 'A hotel cabana boy falls for the wife of a powerful politico. But when she confesses to the affair, her husband determines to end it forever.'),
(706, 'Holiday Heart', '', 'Released', '2.0', '4:3', '24.98', 'R', 2000, 'Drama', '1.33:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A drag queen takes in a drug addict and her daughter and helps raise the daughter.'),
(707, 'Jumanji: The Next Level', 'Columbia Pictures', 'Released', '2.0', '4:3', '74.98', 'NR', 2019, 'Adventure', '1.33:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'As the gang return to Jumanji to rescue one of their own, they discover that nothing is as they expect. The players will have to brave parts unknown and unexplored in order to escape the worldâ€™s most dangerous game.'),
(708, 'Remember Me', 'Create Entertainment', 'Released', '2.0', '4:3', '24.98', 'NR', 2019, 'Comedy', '1.33:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'After discovering his old flame now has Alzheimers, a hopelessly in love widower fakes his way into her senior living community in an effort to reunite with her.'),
(709, 'Love, Simon', 'Temple Hill Entertainment', 'Released', '5.1', '4:3', '24.98', 'NR', 2018, 'Comedy', '1.33:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Everyone deserves a great love story. But for seventeen-year old Simon Spier its a little more complicated: hes yet to tell his family or friends hes gay and he doesnt know the identity of the anonymous classmate hes fallen for online.'),
(710, 'Alita: Battle Angel', 'Troublemaker Studios', 'Released', '2.0', '4:3', '49.98', 'NR', 2019, 'Action', '1.33:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'When Alita awakens with no memory of who she is in a future world she does not recognize, she is taken in by Ido, a compassionate doctor who realizes that somewhere in this abandoned cyborg shell is the heart and soul of a young woman with an extraordinary past.'),
(711, 'All Revved Up', 'Rialto Film', 'Released', '2.0', '4:3', '24.98', 'R', 1998, 'Action', '1.33:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A lovely school teacher finds herself the victim of a scam artist - a garage owner who delights in ripping off his customers. Soon, she has two eager young men, her lizard-loving neighbour and his friend, on her side to help her exact revenge on the sleazy mechanic, who is the leader of a stolen car ring.'),
(712, 'Bagdad Cafe', 'Pro-ject Filmproduktion', 'Released', '2.0', 'LBX, 16:9', '19.98', 'PG', 1987, 'Comedy', '1.33:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A surreal comedy depicting a diverse cast of characters and the changes they undergo as the German tourist Jasmin interacts with each of them at a remote truck stop in the middle of the Mojave desert.'),
(713, 'Black Robe', 'TÃ©lÃ©film Canada', 'Released', 'SUR', 'LBX, 16:9', '19.98', 'R', 1991, 'Adventure', '1.85:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Missionary Father LaForgue travels to the New World in hopes of converting Algonquin Indians to Catholicism. Accepted, though warily, by the Indians, LaForgue travels with the Indians using his strict Catholic rules and ideals to try and impose his religion.'),
(714, 'Claim', 'Sneak Preview Productions', 'Released', '5.1', 'LBX, 16:9', '26.98', 'R', 2013, 'Comedy', '2.35:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Pledging to keep herself from being the oldest and the only woman in her entire family never to wed, Montana embarks on a thirty-day, thirty-thousand-mile expedition to charm a potential suitor into becoming her fiancÃ©.'),
