(976, 'Saint', 'Paramount', 'Released', '5.1', 'LBX, 16:9', '29.99', 'PG-13', 1997, 'Thriller', '2.35:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Simon Templar (The Saint), is a thief for hire, whose latest job to steal the secret process for cold fusion puts him at odds with a traitor bent on toppling the Russian government, as well as the woman who holds its secret.'),
(977, 'Salems Lot', 'New Line Cinema', 'Planned', '1.0', '4:3', '14.98', 'PG', 2022, 'Horror', '1.33:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A new adaptation of Stephen Kings novel.'),
(978, 'Scarecrow', 'Brightlight Pictures', 'Released', '2.0', '4:3', '24.98', 'R', 2013, 'Horror', '1.33:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'For generations, it was an urban legend that lived in the nightmares of children. Now, the season to rejuvenate the tale will revive a towns darkest fears. With the Scarecrow Festival on the horizon, school teacher Aaron Harris is doling out punishment for six students serving detention. Their task: help Aarons girlfriend Amanda fix her family farm before its sold. But the cornfields circling the farm come with a legend and Tyler takes macabre delight in recounting the tale: It never sleeps, it never dies, it cant be stopped, hear their cries.'),
(979, 'Scarface', 'Universal Pictures', 'Released', 'SUR', 'LBX', '34.98', 'R', 1983, 'Action', '2.35:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'After getting a green card in exchange for assassinating a Cuban government official, Tony Montana stakes a claim on the drug trade in Miami. Viciously murdering anyone who stands in his way, Tony eventually becomes the biggest drug lord in the state, controlling nearly all the cocaine that comes through Miami. But increased pressure from the police, wars with Colombian drug cartels and his own drug-fueled paranoia serve to fuel the flames of his eventual downfall.'),
