(982, 'Where Hands Touch', 'Tantrum Films', 'Released', '1.0', '4:3', '24.98', 'NR', 2018, 'War', '1.33:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Germany, 1944. Leyna, the 15-year old daughter of a white German mother and a black African father, meets Lutz, a compassionate member of the Hitler Youth whose father is a prominent Nazi soldier, and they form an unlikely connection in this quickly changing world.'),
