(1116, 'Superstar', 'SNL Studios', 'Released', '5.1', 'LBX, 16:9', '29.99', 'PG-13', 1999, 'Comedy', '1.78:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Orphan Mary Katherine Gallagher, an ugly duckling at St. Monica High School, has a dream: to be kissed soulfully. She decides she can realize this dream if she becomes a superstar, so her prayers, her fantasies, and her conversations with her only friend focus on achieving super-stardom.'),
