(1118, 'Women of Steel', '', 'Released', '2.0', '4:3', '29.97', 'NR', 2020, 'Documentary', '1.33:1', 1, 0, 0, 0, 'Forty years ago, Wollongongâ€™s Jobs for Women Campaign,â€¯withâ€¯directorâ€¯Robynneâ€¯Murphyâ€¯among its leaders,â€¯tookâ€¯onâ€¯Australiaâ€™s most powerfulâ€¯company BHPâ€¯â€“â€¯and won.â€¯But whenâ€¯the 1980s steel slumpâ€¯devastated theâ€¯cityâ€™sâ€¯economy,â€¯the womenâ€¯were forcedâ€¯into the courtroom.â€¯Their struggle plays out against a background of societal changes:â€¯from anti-discrimination legislation,â€¯to theâ€¯shiftingâ€¯rolesâ€¯of women in theâ€¯homeâ€¯and workforceâ€¯(particularly complex in Wollongongâ€™s migrant,â€¯non-English speaking households).â€¯This fascinatingâ€¯account of the largely forgotten history of Australiaâ€™s Steel City was crafted over decades with support from local community volunteers andâ€¯over 500â€¯donors.â€¯ â€¯'),
(1119, 'Swashbuckler', 'Universal Pictures', 'Released', '1.0', 'LBX, 16:9', '24.98', 'PG', 1976, 'Adventure', '2.35:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A pirate and a hot-tempered noblewoman join forces to protect Jamaica from a tyrant.'),
(1120, 'Sweet Hereafter', 'Alliance Communications', 'Released', '5.1', '4:3, LBX, 16:9', '24.98', 'R', 1997, 'Drama', '2.35:1', 2, 0, 0, 0, 'A small mountain community in Canada is devastated when a school bus accident leaves more than a dozen of its children dead. A big-city lawyer arrives to help the survivors and victims families prepare a class-action suit, but his efforts only seem to push the townspeople further apart. At the same time, one teenage survivor of the accident has to reckon with the loss of innocence brought about by a different kind of damage.'),
(1121, 'Switchback', 'Rysher Entertainment', 'Released', '5.1', 'LBX', '29.99', 'R', 1997, 'Thriller', '2.35:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'FBI agent Dennis Quaid tries to catch a serial killer who kidnapped his son.'),
(1122, 'Taffin', 'Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer', 'Released', '2.0', '4:3, LBX', '24.98', 'R', 1988, 'Action', '1.85:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'When a small Irish town is terrorized by a corrupt business syndicate, a lone hero (Brosnan) wages an all out war.'),
(1123, 'Taking Of Pelham One Two Three', 'Palladium', 'Released', '1.0', 'LBX', '24.98', 'R', 1974, 'Action', '2.35:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'In New York, armed men hijack a subway car and demand a ransom for the passengers. Even if its paid, how could they get away?'),
(1124, 'Talented Mr. Ripley', 'Timnick Films', 'Released', '5.1', 'LBX, 16:9', '29.99', 'R', 1999, 'Thriller', '1.85:1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Tom Ripley is a calculating young man who believes its better to be a fake somebody than a real nobody. Opportunity knocks in the form of a wealthy U.S. shipbuilder who hires Tom to travel to Italy to bring back his playboy son, Dickie. Ripley worms his way into the idyllic lives of Dickie and his girlfriend, plunging into a daring scheme of duplicity, lies and murder.'),
